ARM: davinci: add support for am1808 based EnBW CMC board

This board supports:

- AM1808 based board
- 64 MiB DDR ram
- 2 MiB Nor flash
- 128 MiB NAND flash
- use internal RTC
- I2C support
- hwmon lm75 support
- UBI/UBIFS support
- MMC support
- USB OTG support

This patch adds the basic DTS file enabling the serial ports.
Other features will be added in due course of time.

